/description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 02:23:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国4月工业增加值增长6.7% 超预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-april-industrial-output-rises-67-beats-expectations-2024-05-17/</link><description>随着制造业复苏步伐加快，4 月份中国工业产出同比增长 6.7%，增速较 3 月份的 4.5%有所加快。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 02:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-april-industrial-output-rises-67-beats-expectations-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>代理顾问格拉斯刘易斯敦促赫斯股东接受雪佛龙的收购要约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/proxy-adviser-glass-lewis-urges-hess-shareholders-accept-chevron-takeover-offer-2024-05-17/</link><description>代理顾问格拉斯·刘易斯 (Glass Lewis) 周四表示，赫斯股东应在该石油公司 5 月 28 日的特别会议上投票支持雪佛龙 530 亿美元的全股票收购要约。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:22:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/proxy-adviser-glass-lewis-urges-hess-shareholders-accept-chevron-takeover-offer-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>追踪中国在台湾上空的“灰色地带”热气球飞行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tracking-chinas-grey-zone-balloon-flights-over-taiwan-2024-05-17/</link><description>大约在台湾一月份总统大选前一个月，中国开始向台湾海峡派遣入侵者：100多个气球，其中一些飞越台湾领空或台北控制的繁忙的民航空中走廊。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tracking-chinas-grey-zone-balloon-flights-over-taiwan-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国经济放缓迹象，美元每周下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-set-weekly-drop-us-slowdown-signs-2024-05-17/</link><description>由于通胀降温和美国经济疲软的迹象提高了降息的可能性，美元兑欧元周五出现两个半月来最大单周跌幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:13:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-set-weekly-drop-us-slowdown-signs-2024-05-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国数据转储前市场乐观</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-16/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 21:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪推迟2025年智利锂正极工厂计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-byd-postpones-plans-2025-chile-lithium-cathode-plant-2024-05-16/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪公司美洲区负责人周二对路透表示，该公司推迟了 2025 年在智利生产电动汽车 (EV) 电池锂阴极的计划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 18:29:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-byd-postpones-plans-2025-chile-lithium-cathode-plant-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称，美国国防部长计划在新加坡会见中国国防部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defense-chief-plans-meet-with-chinese-counterpart-singapore-us-official-says-2024-05-16/</link><description>一位美国官员周四表示，美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀预计将于本月晚些时候在新加坡举行的一次会议上会见中国国防部长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:38:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-defense-chief-plans-meet-with-chinese-counterpart-singapore-us-official-says-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>普京中国之行的主要收获</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/top-takeaways-putins-trip-china-2024-05-16/</link><description>俄罗斯总统普京周四对中国进行国事访问，受到中国国家主席习近平的迎接。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:44:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/top-takeaways-putins-trip-china-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>西门子能源总裁表示没有中国就不可能实现能源转型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-boss-says-there-can-be-no-energy-transition-without-china-2024-05-16/</link><description>西门子能源公司首席执行官表示，欧洲能源行业过于依赖中国，无法考虑去风险化的想法，这反映出该行业需要世界第二大经济体供应的困境，但并不需要随之而来的竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-boss-says-there-can-be-no-energy-transition-without-china-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>白宫布雷纳德表示，中国的出口可能会削弱对美国的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/white-houses-brainard-says-chinas-exports-can-undermine-investments-us-2024-05-16/</link><description>白宫国家经济顾问莱尔·布雷纳德周四表示，中国某些行业的工业产能和出口规模如此之大，可能会损害美国投资的可行性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 15:54:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/white-houses-brainard-says-chinas-exports-can-undermine-investments-us-2024-05-16/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，汇丰最大投资者中国平安正在考虑减持股份的选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbcs-biggest-investor-ping-an-mulls-options-cut-stake-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-05-16/</link><description>彭博社周四援引知情人士的话报道称，汇丰银行的最大股东中国平安保险正在考虑减持这家专注于亚洲的银行 8% 的股份。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 15:36:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbcs-biggest-investor-ping-an-mulls-options-cut-stake-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-05-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>